<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>How MediCheck Works</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css"> <!-- Link your main stylesheet here -->
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #f4f4f4;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: #fff;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .step {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .step h2 {
      color: #34495e;
    }

    .step p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #555;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #8e44ad;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .footer-note {
      text-align: center;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    /* Tablets (max-width: 768px) */
@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
  .container {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .step h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .step p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
}
/* Mobile phones (max-width: 480px) */
@media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
  .container {
    padding: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .step h2 {
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .step p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .footer-note {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
}
  </style>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header.ejs') %>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>How MediCheck Works</h1>

    <div class="step">
      <h2>1. Create an Account or Log In</h2>
      <p>
        To get the best experience, <span class="highlight">sign up or log in</span> to your MediCheck account. This lets you save your health records, view past diagnoses, and get personalized suggestions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <h2>2. Enter Your Symptoms</h2>
      <p>
        On the <span class="highlight">Diagnose</span> page, describe your symptoms by selecting them from the list or typing them in. Be as accurate as possible to get better recommendations.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <h2>3. Get Instant Analysis</h2>
      <p>
        MediCheck instantly analyzes your symptoms using intelligent logic and offers possible conditions or health issues. You’ll also see recommended treatments, medications, or steps to take.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <h2>4. Locate Nearby Clinics</h2>
      <p>
        If the condition needs professional attention, we’ll help you find <span class="highlight">nearby clinics or hospitals</span> so you can take immediate action.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="footer-note">
      MediCheck is not a replacement for professional medical advice. Always consult a doctor when unsure.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
